{"tid":2278274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★社會房屋企業 計劃在天水圍興建「光村」 條件：要有一門手藝","createTime":"2020-11-09T04:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-09T14:32:13.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60f8ecc5160112b7a9715c81d451afdf91e0e4d0","tid":2278274,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】社會房屋企業「要有光」計劃在天水圍興建「光村」，提供約100個單位，租期不多於三年，會參照南丫島「光房」的新青年鄉村模式發展，協助有短期貧窮戶以創意轉化為向上流動力。<br />\n<br />\n八十後的阿盈年多前與兒子搬進南丫島的「手藝人光房」，<span class=\"xx-large\">條件之一是要有一門手藝</span>可以支撐生活。<br />\n<br />\n阿盈做過產品開發及設計，屋內擺設由她一手包辦，除了定期會有皮革工作坊，她更將自己的手作擺賣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412133&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BWipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=0db0d5cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D412133&h=5a9c2cae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=412133</a>"},{"pid":"b78f0bd48085eb1833e9db8a2f4b6bb416a3df5a","tid":2278274,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"why 要一門手藝？<br />\n<br />\n張英 張活游 粵語片年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e4aec4cd67a53c3ee7e17b5fe25bccd2ce6b55","tid":2278274,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78f0bd48085eb1833e9db8a2f4b6bb416a3df5a","tid":2278274,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T04:57:22.000Z","msg":"why 要一門手藝？<br />\n<br />\n張英 張活游 粵語片年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im